text.section:
The following revenue shall be credited to the fund:
Four dollars ($4) of the annual registration fee for each registered motorcycle as provided in KRS 186.050;
Four dollars ($4) of the application fee for a motorcycle instruction permit as provided in KRS 186.531;
Four dollars ($4) of the fee for each original or renewal motorcycle driver's license or endorsement as provided in KRS 186.531; and
Any federal or state motorcycle safety funds granted to the program.
